---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="DealMela's affiliate relationships and how we earn commissions on the deals we feature."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 pt-10 sm:pt-14 pb-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-ink-faint mb-8">Last updated: [Admin to set date]</p>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gold-soft border border-gold/30 px-4 py-3 mb-8 text-sm text-ink-soft">
      <strong class="text-ink">Draft scaffold, not final legal text.</strong> This page is written to standard affiliate-disclosure structure so the site is compliant from launch, but the Admin (or a qualified professional) should review and confirm the wording before going live — DealMela is not a law firm and this isn't legal advice.
    </div>

    <div class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed space-y-5 text-[15px] sm:text-base">
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Amazon Associates</h2>
      <p>
        As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. DealMela is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.in.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink pt-2">Other retail partners</h2>
      <p>
        DealMela also participates in affiliate programs with Flipkart and other Indian retailers, in some cases through affiliate aggregator networks. When you click a "View Deal" or "Check Current Price" button on this site and go on to make a purchase, DealMela may earn a commission from the retailer. This does not affect the price you pay.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink pt-2">How this affects what we publish</h2>
      <p>
        Every product featured on DealMela is chosen because we believe the price and quality genuinely stand out — commission rates do not influence which products we select or how we rank them. Ratings, review counts, and prices shown are sourced directly from the retailer's own listing and labeled accordingly; we do not generate or alter this data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink pt-2">Identifying sponsored content</h2>
      <p>
        Every "View Deal" and "Check Current Price" button on this site is marked with a short "Ad" label indicating a paid/affiliate relationship, in line with ASCI (Advertising Standards Council of India) guidance on disclosure of material connections. Outbound links to retailers use <code class="text-xs bg-gold-soft px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">rel="sponsored"</code>, per search engines' own guidance for paid links.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink pt-2">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If anything on this page is unclear, or you'd like more detail on a specific listing's sourcing, reach out via the <a href="/contact" class="text-brick underline underline-offset-2">Contact</a> page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
